  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Jeevan Action Decision",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As a video of Norwood Pradeshiya Sabha member Susai Alexander threatening and assaulting a common man standing in a queue of gas cylinders is going viral on social media, the general secretary of the party Jeevan Thondaman has said that an inquiry will be held against him and till then he will be suspended from the party. .",
        "The media wing of the Congress has announced that the high-level disciplinary committee of the Sri Lanka Workers' Congress will soon conduct an investigation into the controversies and allegations against Norwood Regional Council member Soosai Alexander.",
        "Jeevan Thondaman, Secretary General of EC, has said that EC will never allow such activities and all the party membership rights of the said Pradeshiya Sabha member have been temporarily revoked with effect."
      ],
